data.title: DJ Khaled Just Bought Robbie Williams's Home for $9.9 Million
data.meta_description: The over-the-top Beverly Hills mansion has seven bedrooms and 11 baths
data.text:
When buying a house in one of California's celebrity-favored neighborhoods, it's more than likely that there will be a famous connection. This huge mansion has double the star power—DJ Khaled just purchased the $9.9 million home from British singer Robbie Williams, reports Trulia. The 10,681-square-foot residence is certainly fit for the rapper and social media star's lavish tastes, with seven bedrooms and a whopping 11 baths, a two-floor entry hall, a formal dining room, an expansive kitchen with a butler's pantry and maid's quarters, and a gym/media room. Outside, there are two terraced patios as well as an outdoor kitchen and a pool and spa. DJ Khaled definitely has the (house) keys to success.
